data.title: Following her Las Vegas residency, #Adele is ready for a break. The “Easy On Me” singer shared that her “tank is quite empty” after her...
data.meta_description:
5,972 likes, 124 comments - hollywoodreporter on July 16, 2024: "Following her Las Vegas residency, #Adele is ready for a break. The “Easy On Me” singer shared that her “tank is quite empty” after her lengthy run of performances—an emotional experience that, while profound, has depleted her energy. ⁠
⁠
“I want a big break after all this and I think I want to do other creative things just for a little while," she says. "You know, I don’t even sing at home at all. How strange is that?” For more on the star's statements, head to the link in bio.".
